  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00001",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "织女上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00002",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "浪淘沙",
      "speakers": [
        "织女"
      ],
      "text": "云护玉梭儿，巧织机丝，天宫原不管相思。报道今宵七夕，忽忆年时。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00003",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "织女"
      ],
      "text": "纤云弄巧，飞星传恨，银汉秋光暗度。金风玉露一相逢，便胜却人间无数。柔肠似水，佳期如梦，遥指鹊桥前路。两情若是久长时，又岂在朝朝暮暮。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00004",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "织女"
      ],
      "text": "我乃天孙织女是也。蒙上帝谕旨，与牛郎结为天上夫妇。年年七夕，渡河相见。今乃下界天宝十载，七月七夕。你看银河无浪，喜鹊将填，不免暂撤机丝，整妆而待。",
      "text_length": 73
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00005",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "织女梳妆毕。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00006",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "山桃花",
      "speakers": [
        "织女"
      ],
      "text": "俺这里乍跑锦字，暂驾香辎。趁碧落无云滞，新凉暮飔，踹上这桥影参差，俯映着河光净止。更喜杀新月纤，花露湿，低绕喜鹊双飞翅也。",
      "text_length": 61
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00007",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "牛郎上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00008",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "山桃花",
      "speakers": [
        "牛郎"
      ],
      "text": "只觉得银汉秋生别样姿。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00009",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛郎"
      ],
      "text": "天孙一向安否？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00010",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "织女"
      ],
      "text": "仙郎别来无恙。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00011",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛郎"
      ],
      "text": "我与你天上良缘，一年一度，皆赖上帝恩赐也。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00012",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "织女"
      ],
      "text": "便是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00013",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛郎"
      ],
      "text": "你看星河之下，香烟缭绕，云雾腾空，却是何处？",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00014",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "织女"
      ],
      "text": "是唐天子与杨妃在长生殿乞巧。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00015",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛郎"
      ],
      "text": "天孙，看她们一片诚心，和你到彼一望。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00016",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "织女"
      ],
      "text": "请。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00017",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同山桃花",
      "speakers": [
        "牛郎",
        "织女"
      ],
      "text": "天上留佳会，年年在斯。却笑他人世，情怨顷刻时。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00018",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "织女、牛郎同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00019",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "设鹊桥、百鸟、玩艺、月宫、云片、彩切。杨玉环上。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00020",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "二郎神",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "宫廷金炉篆霭，烛光掩映，米大蜘蛛，喜冰盘种荳，花枝招展银瓶。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00021",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众宫女同设香案。杨玉环拈香。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00022",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "妾身杨玉环，虔诚心香，拜告双星，伏乞鉴佑。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00023",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "二郎神",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "愿钗盒情缘久订，莫使做秋风冷扇。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00024",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众内监执扇伞同上，李隆基上。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00025",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "二郎神",
      "speakers": [
        "李隆基"
      ],
      "text": "好一片皓月当天。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00026",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "妾身接驾。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00027",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李隆基"
      ],
      "text": "梓童平身。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00028",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "今因七夕佳期，敬排香果，特设天孙乞巧。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00029",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李隆基"
      ],
      "text": "却是爱卿至诚。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00030",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "惶恐。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00031",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李隆基"
      ],
      "text": "唉，叹双星一年一度，岂无离恨。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00032",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "陛下言及双星别恨，使妾凄然，只可惜人间不知天上的事。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00033",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "二郎神",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "如打听，决疑了相思成病。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00034",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杨玉环哭。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00035",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "妾思牛郎织女，虽则七夕一度，却是地久天长。只恐陛下与妾的恩情，不能够似他们长远。",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00036",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李隆基"
      ],
      "text": "同心合意，不离龙床，时刻之思，心可知矣。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00037",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "臣妾受恩深重，今夜有句话儿。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00038",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李隆基"
      ],
      "text": "讲来。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00039",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "妾蒙宠眷，六宫无比，只怕日久恩疏，难免白首之叹。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00040",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "二郎神",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "提起便心痛，念寒微侍夜廷，更依傍辇多荣幸。瞬息间怕花谢春去际，实难凭，论恩情，若得个久长时，死也幸。若得个到头时，死也瞑，抵多少平阳歌舞，恩移爱更，长门孤寂寞，暗涕零，断肠枉泣红颜命。",
      "text_length": 92
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00041",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李隆基"
      ],
      "text": "孤与你好似比目之鱼，爱妃何必多虑。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00042",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "既蒙陛下如此情浓，趁此双星之下，乞赐盟约，一见始终。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00043",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李隆基"
      ],
      "text": "如此香案伺候。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00044",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "领旨。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00045",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众内监、众宫女同设罢。〖吹打〗。牛郎、织女同上，同上桌子。百鸟彩切托明月。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00046",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同猫儿坠",
      "speakers": [
        "李隆基",
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "香肩斜靠，携手下阶行，一片因何当殿横，罗衣陡觉夜凉生。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00047",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "愿得你我福寿齐，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00048",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "李隆基"
      ],
      "text": "在地同为连理枝。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00049",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "天长地久情无尽，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00050",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "李隆基"
      ],
      "text": "此誓绵绵永佳期。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00051",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李隆基、杨玉环同拜，同起。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00052",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "妾感陛下今夕之盟，死生守之矣。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00053",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "猫儿坠",
      "speakers": [
        "李隆基"
      ],
      "text": "喜今夕同把心结，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00054",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "猫儿坠",
      "speakers": [
        "杨玉环"
      ],
      "text": "问今夜有谁折证？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00055",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众內监、众宫女引李隆基、杨玉环同下。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00056",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "猫儿坠",
      "speakers": [
        "牛郎"
      ],
      "text": "只见他盟誓密，此拜祷孜孜，两情洽无二意，同一词。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00057",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛郎"
      ],
      "text": "天孙，你看唐天子与贵妃，好不恩爱也。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00058",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "猫儿坠",
      "speakers": [
        "牛郎"
      ],
      "text": "俏相偎倚着香肩没些缝儿。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00059",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛郎"
      ],
      "text": "我与你既缔天上良缘，当做情场管领，况二人向我等说誓，须当保护。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00060",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "猫儿坠",
      "speakers": [
        "牛郎"
      ],
      "text": "见了他恋比翼慕并枝，愿生生世世，情真至也，合令他长作人间风月司。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00061",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "织女"
      ],
      "text": "只是他二人劫难将至，免不得生离死别，若果后来不能背今盟，决当为之管合。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00062",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛郎"
      ],
      "text": "天孙之言有理。你看夜色将阑，且回斗牛宫去者。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00063",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "织女"
      ],
      "text": "请。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00064",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同猫儿坠",
      "speakers": [
        "牛郎",
        "织女"
      ],
      "text": "天上留佳会，年年在斯。却笑他人世，情缘顷刻时。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006062_e00065",
      "play_id": "02006062",
      "scene_id": "02006062_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "牛郎、织女相扶下。",
      "text_length": 9
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}